    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER A WORLD</h2>Explore the potion shop Wilds risen out of The Cascade.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115180/extras/c0d0a998da4f80d2ea56925581a16843.avif?t=1734045669\" width=616 height=113 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HEAL A TORN LANDSCAPE</h2>Uncover the mystery of the lost shopkeeper.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115180/extras/23055a4065e2843c10286c2583014732.avif?t=1734045669\" width=616 height=113 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POTION APPRENTICE</h2>Seek out recipes and harvest ingredients to make potions and unlock abilities<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115180/extras/8fce65e44614b98a0d36064e5435fb7c.avif?t=1734045669\" width=616 height=112 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHANGE APPEARANCE</h2>Unlock character parts for a new look.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115180/extras/f928b89d5d3a7b9fff6984e197159b09.avif?t=1734045669\" width=616 height=112 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAIN KNOWLEDGE AND SKILLS</h2>Upgrade weapons and tools<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115180/extras/281098b83f279ec586504b6defa7c53a.avif?t=1734045669\" width=616 height=112 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE A NETWORK OF GROW FIELDS</h2>As your Field network grows so do those of your rivals elsewhere in the shop.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115180/extras/8ee15002da6353fedbb1f157dba10788.avif?t=1734045669\" width=616 height=113 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BRIBE A RIVAL</h2>Make a Bribe for a rival to change their opinion to agree with yours.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115180/extras/678e80fd8db88ef6624b55e898dc19e9.avif?t=1734045669\" width=616 height=113 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY PIECES</h2>Uncover what happened to the shopkeeper, meet the villagers, encounter rivals and write your own self into the place.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115180/extras/e0bb56479666cabc75db210451471700.avif?t=1734045669\" width=616 height=113 /></span>",
